        "ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_4": "<p>Can I take it while pregnant or breastfeeding?</p>",
        "ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_5": "<p>Is it made in Canada?</p>",
        "ggx4WepX4ed_text": "<p>Yes. Many customers switch from coffee to Vanilla Matcha Collagen because it delivers steady, focused energy without jitters or crashes. It’s a smoother alternative to traditional caffeine.</p>",
